{"id":"ithrite","term":"Ithrite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Two of David’s warriors so designated (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:38\">2 Sam. 23:38</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:40\">1 Chr. 11:40</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 23:38","1 Chronicles 11:40"]}